meta {
  name: Find by date and currency config_exchange-rate
  type: http
  seq: 7
}

get {
  url: {{host}}/api/config/{{bu_code}}/exchange-rate/by-date/:date/:currency_code
  body: none
  auth: bearer
}

headers {
  x-app-id: {{x_app_id}}
}

auth:bearer {
  token: {{access_token}}
}

query {
  ~version: 
}

docs {
  ## Get Exchange Rate by Date and Currency Code
  ดึงข้อมูลอัตราแลกเปลี่ยนตามวันที่และรหัสสกุลเงิน

  Retrieves the exchange rate for a specific date and currency code.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `bu_code` | string | Business unit code |
  | `date` | string (yyyy-MM-dd) | Exchange rate date |
  | `currency_code` | string | Currency code (ISO 4217, e.g. USD) |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  | Permission key | Roles |
  |---------------|-------|
  | `configuration.exchange_rate:view` | All authenticated users |

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
      "at_date": "2026-01-16",
      "currency_id": "93dabe25-1668-4c5b-bceb-3e0b83b78002",
      "currency_code": "USD",
      "currency_name": "US Dollar",
      "exchange_rate": 35.5,
      "note": "Daily rate update",
      "info": null,
      "created_at": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z",
      "updated_at": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 404 | No exchange rate found for given date and currency code |
  > Service-layer errors propagate via TCP; see micro-business for full list.
}

params:path {
  date: 2026-01-16
  currency_code: USD
}
